name: The Data Drug
description:
The unique 1/1 GHOST EDITION of the fifth album from TENGUSHEE.

'The Data Drug'

Purchase includes the GHOST EDITION of poetry anthology 'Spiritu Dei Sub Terra' (PDF) by Tengushee complete with an introduction to "the spirit of the underground", + 2 extra tracks not available on any other edition or platform unique to this NFT ('Ghost' & 'Finished').
